token_info.name: RGBCMYKW (hDAO Collection)
token_info.description: Created by @MathMakesArt (https://mathmakes.art) on 2021/05/31. The grid shows a discretized venn diagram of the 8 colors which can be represented by a 3-bit-per-pixel RGB encoding. This is a special mint for the NFTz (@_NFTz) hDAO Collection, which also features pieces from @mumu_thestan, @dereknft, @vjthor, and @ChrisRandallAr1. Written in p5.js and minted as HTML.
